COMMERCIAL USE OF THE BENCHMARK

The benchmark — including the simulation framework, the 41 personas of Tello,
the 7-layer sociolinguistic prompt, the 10-dialogue ground truth, and the
experimental templates — is released openly for non-commercial use.

Commercial use (including but not limited to: paid products or services that
incorporate the benchmark, derivative commercial datasets, or paid consulting
that materially relies on the benchmark) requires explicit attribution to the
author and prior written permission.

Attribution format:
  Urrutia Salcedo, J. N. (2026). Sociedad Opita Benchmark (v1.0).
  https://github.com/nicourrutia98/sociedad-opita

For commercial licensing inquiries, contact the author via GitHub
(@nicourrutia98) or Instagram (@nico98urrutia).
